A lone figure sits in meditation posture atop an endless spiral staircase that loops back on itself like an Escher drawing, rendered in warm Studio Ghibli watercolor style. The staircase floats in a dreamy twilight sky filled with soft peach and lavender clouds. Golden coins and luxury items slowly transform into glowing butterflies as they drift upward from the lower steps, dissolving into light. The meditating person has their hands open, releasing more butterflies toward distant floating islands where tiny figures help each other climb. The overall mood is contemplative and hopeful, with characteristic Ghibli soft lighting, organic flowing lines, and that signature sense of quiet wonder. Delicate cherry blossom petals swirl gently through the scene, connecting all elements in a continuous flowing motion.
